---
title: Dill & Parmesan Crumbed Fish with Lemon Pepper Kumara Wedges
description: This dish has stepped it up a notch and transformed the idea of classic fish and chips with tender fish fillets coated in a crunchy dill-Parmesan crumb. With a side of lemon pepper-spiced kumara wedges and a refreshing salad - it really doesn't get any better than this.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/dill-parmesan-crumbed-fish-32b39ed0.jpg
